PROCLIB

A library for system information.

Files:
    -proc.h: main header
    -proc.c: implementation of common functions
    -proc_cpu.h: header for the cpu info functions
    -proc_cpu.c: implementation of the cpu info functions
    -proc_mem.h: header for the memory info functions
    -proc_mem.c: implementation of the memory info functions

Common Fuctions:
    -char*  proc_search_keyword(char* file, char* keyword): looks in file
    for the value associated with keyword
    -int proc_num_of_occ(char* file, char* keyword): looks for the number
    of occurences of keyword in file

CPU Info Functions:
    -char* proc_cpu_vendor(): returns the vendor of the 1st CPU
    -char* proc_cpu_model(): returns the name of the CPU

Memory Info Functions:
    -int proc_mem_total(proc_mem_unit unit): returns the total memory in
    the unit associated with unit
    -int proc_mem_free(proc_mem_unit unit): returns the amount of free
    memory in unit
